rows.label: qst201819_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello, Phonex-san. There's
something I'd like to ask you...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0002
rows.name:
Go away! I have nothing to
say to the likes of you!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0003
rows.name:
Please don't say that...
This is an emergency.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0004
rows.name:
Just for a little bit, please
listen to what I have to say!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0005
rows.name: No way. I don't trust humans. Go home!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0006
rows.name:
Hmm, this is a problem... He
won't listen to me at all.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0007
rows.name:
Maybe we should go back to Mimi's
place and think of a plan.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0008
rows.name: Mimi might know a good way.
